title: New: Blackbird Blackbird – New Leaf
content:
It’s been a while since we last heard from the prolific Blackbird Blackbird, and it appears that in that time he’s been keeping pretty busy.

Having toyed with the concept of putting out stems for a previously unreleased track for people to remix, Mikey has dropped a new cut in the form of the deliriously upbeat New Leaf. At six and a half minutes long, there’s plenty to immerse yourself in, amongst the jangly electronic sections and reverb-laden vocals. Download the stems here, and check out New Leaf below.

New Leaf by BLACKBIRD BLACKBIRD
